FICON Express16S+ FICON Express16S+ (carry forward to IBM z16) supports a link data rate of 16 Gbps and auto negotiation to 4 or 8 Gbps for synergy with switches, directors, and storage devices. With support for native FICON, High-Performance FICON for Z (zHPF), and Fibre Channel Protocol (FCP), the IBM Z enable you to position your SAN for even higher performance, which helps you to prepare for an end-to-end 16 Gbps infrastructure to meet the lower latency and increased bandwidth demands of your applications. The new FICON Express16S+ channel works with your fiber optic cabling environment (single mode and multimode optical cables).
